  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameGenerator
    A class which plays a certain number of Ataxx games with the given conditions.
    StatsMain
    The purpose of this class is to play ataxx a given number of times and to output the victory stats of two intelligent players playing with different parameters.
    TournamentMain
    This class plays a tournament between 64 different ComplexEvaluators, and logs the winner.
